    Implementation of YOLOv2 classifier based on the article: https://arxiv.org/pdf/1612.08242.pdf Created by Zoltan Szabo on 12/17/17. https://github.com/szaza/android-yolo-v2

      • classifyImage

        public java.util.List<Recognition> classifyImage(float[] tensorFlowOutput,
                                                 java.util.Vector<java.lang.String> labels)
        It classifies the object/objects on the image
        パラメータ:
        tensorFlowOutput - output from the tensorflow, it is a 13x13x125 tensor 125 = (numClass + Tx, Ty, Tw, Th, To) * 5 - cause we have 5 boxes per each cell
        labels - a string vector with the labels
        戻り値:
        a list of recognition objects
